name: Open source physiotherapy
tagline: A project for an open source physiotherapy curriculum.
body:
### Welcome to Open Source Physiotherapy.
This is the GitHub home of a project that aims to create an open source physiotherapy curriculum that can be reproduced, edited and re-shared with others.

### Authors and Contributors
This project is currently maintained by Michael Rowe, a physiotherapy lecturer at the University of the Western Cape in Cape Town, South Africa.
